cu.explanation_en: Setting the local SCTP port for DU to an out-of-range value (99999) will cause SCTP binding failure and prevent F1 interface establishment.

du.explanation_en: Setting msg3_DeltaPreamble to an out-of-range value (100) will cause invalid preamble power configuration and RACH procedure failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 msg3_DeltaPreamble 設定為超出範圍的值 (100)，會導致無效的前導碼功率配置，並造成 RACH 程序失敗。
